Package: vst-installer
Version: 0.0.1
Architecture: amd64
Depends: zenity, wine
Description: GUI wrapper to install Native Instruments VSTs using Wine and yabridge.
 A small utility that mounts plugin ISOs, runs the Windows installer under Wine,
 and triggers a yabridge sync where available.